
Infra

This folder contains all the infrastructure stuff (scripts, etc) required to check Pivot sources, and all other steps needed to create a Release.

  There are some subdirectories here:

     bin/
       UNIX shell scripts

     deb/
       Stuff required to create a Debian package (.deb) for Pivot

     doap/
       Stuff related to DOAP files for Pivot, see http://projects.apache.org/doap.html

     lib/
       Utility libraries, like RAT

     rpm/
       Stuff required to create a Red Hat package (.rpm) for Pivot



